<style type="text/css">
p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px Helvetica}
p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px Helvetica; min-height: 22.0px}
p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px Helvetica}
p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px Helvetica; min-height: 14.0px}
p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px Helvetica}
p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 9.0px Monaco; min-height: 12.0px}
p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 9.0px Monaco}
p.p8 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 9.0px Monaco; color: #606060}
p.p9 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 9.0px Monaco; color: #0030a9; min-height: 12.0px}
p.p10 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 9.0px Monaco; color: #0030a9}
span.s1 {color: #0030a9}
span.s2 {color: #000000}
span.s3 {color: #0023b5}
span.s4 {color: #606060}
span.Apple-tab-span {white-space:pre}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<p class="p1"><b>AppClock</b></p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p3"><b>superclase: Clock</b></p>
<p class="p4"><br></p>
<p class="p5">SystemClock es mas preciso, pero no puede llamar primitivos de Cocoa.</p>
<p class="p5">AppClock es menos preciso (usa NSTimers) pero puede llamar primitivos de Cocoa.</p>
<p class="p4"><br></p>
<p class="p5">Se necesita usar el SystemClock para tener planificaciones precisas/musicales.</p>
<p class="p6"><br></p>
<p class="p6"><br></p>
<p class="p6"><br></p>
<p class="p5"><b>*sched(delta,task)<span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>//<span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>*planificar(delta, tarea)</b></p>
<p class="p5"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>el número decimal que se devuelve es el delta (tiempo) con el cual se replanificará la función</p>
<p class="p6"><br></p>
<p class="p7"><span class="s1"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>AppClock</span>.sched(0.0,{ arg tiempo;<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p8"><span class="s2"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></span>["AppClock ha estado tocando por ",tiempo]<span class="s2">.postln;<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></span></p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>rrand(0.1,0.9)<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>});</p>
<p class="p6"><br></p>
<p class="p5"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>devolver nil impedirá que la tarea sea replanificada.</p>
<p class="p6"><br></p>
<p class="p7"><span class="s1"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>AppClock</span>.sched(2.0,{<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p8"><span class="s2"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></span>"2.0 segundos despues"<span class="s2">.postln;<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></span></p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="s1">nil</span><span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>});</p>
<p class="p6"><br></p>
<p class="p5"><b>*clear<span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>//<span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>*borrar</b></p>
<p class="p5"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>borra el planificador del AppClock para detenerlo</p>
<p class="p9"><br></p>
<p class="p10"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>AppClock<span class="s2">.clear</span></p>
<p class="p6"><br></p>
<p class="p5"><b>*play(task)<span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>//<span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>*tocar(tarea)</b></p>
<p class="p5"><b><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></b>La tarea/Routine (Rutina) arroja un valor decimal (de punto flotante) indicando el delta (segundos)<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p5"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>que AppClock debe esperar hasta retomar la Routine</p>
<p class="p6"><br></p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>(</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="s3">var</span> w, r;</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>w = <span class="s3">Window</span>.new(<span class="s4">"temblor"</span>, <span class="s3">Rect</span>(512, 256, 360, 130));</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>w.front;</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>r = <span class="s3">Routine</span>({ <span class="s3">arg</span> tiempoAppClock;</p>
<p class="p8"><span class="s2"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>[</span>"AppClock ha estado tocando durante estos segundos:"<span class="s2">,tiempoAppClock].postln;</span></p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>60.do({ <span class="s3">arg</span> i;</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>0.05.yield;</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>w.bounds = w.bounds.moveBy(10.rand2, 10.rand2);</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>w.alpha = cos(i*0.1pi)*0.5+0.5;</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>});</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>1.yield;</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>w.close;</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>});</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="s3">AppClock</span>.play(r);</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>)</p>
<p class="p6"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></p>
<p class="p5"><b>*tick<span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>//<span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>*tic<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></b></p>
<p class="p5"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>AppClock.tick es llamado periodicamente por la misma aplicación SuperCollider.</p>
<p class="p5"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>Esto actualiza el Scheduler (planificador) y causa que cualquier tarea (task) planeada<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p5"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>se ejecute. Nunca debe uno mismo llamar este método.</p>
<p class="p4"><br></p>
<p class="p4"><br></p>
</body>
</html>
